# Painless-CRM signed webhooks — local `wrangler dev` config.
#
# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` and fill in real values. `.dev.vars` is
# gitignored; NEVER commit real secrets. In production these live in the
# Cloudflare dashboard (plain vars) / `wrangler secret put` (CRM_WEBHOOK_SECRET).
#
# SECURITY: none of these may be exposed to the browser. Do NOT add a PUBLIC_
# prefix and do NOT read them via import.meta.env in client code. All HMAC
# signing happens server-side in the Worker (src/lib/crm/signer.ts).

# Shared HMAC secret — 32+ chars. MUST be byte-identical to the CRM's value.
CRM_WEBHOOK_SECRET="replace-with-32+char-shared-secret-aaaaaaaa"

# CRM base URL — no trailing slash.
CRM_BASE_URL="https://crm.staging.painless.example"

# CRM tenant uuid — sent as `company_id` in every webhook body.
CRM_COMPANY_ID="00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"

# Optional — overrides the envelope `source` field (defaults to "website").
# CRM_WEBHOOK_SOURCE="website"

# Optional — pricing version uuid injected into the /quote webhook's
# `quote.pricing_version_id`. Leave unset to omit the optional quote block.
# CRM_PRICING_VERSION_ID="00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
